SENATE AMENDMENT

SENATE AMENDMENT “ ” to COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “A” to S.P. 401, L.D. 911
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment clarifies when an election remains an election determined by ranked-
33 choice voting if a candidate dies, is disqualified or withdraws less than 70 days before an
44 election and clarifies the ranked-choice voting count procedures in these instances.
